      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait, if i take 10 units and my snack was only an hour ago, won't that cause a massive spike and then a huge drop? i'm reading some stuff online about insulin stacking and how taking too much too fast can be really dangerous. are you sure 10 is the right amount even if my sensitivity factor is 1:50? i'm worried about the math you're using.",
